    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ここで役作りを\nするんですか？",
      "startTime": 164.0889794389,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.8223056514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。バイクのシーンは基本的にCGを使うし\n撮影でもスタントマンの方が乗るんだが……",
      "startTime": 169.7333319982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それでも、琴乃自身がバイクに乗ってみることで\n感じるものがあるんじゃないかと思ってな",
      "startTime": 176.2999986649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 179.0509224612
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "でも……ここ、ゲームセンターですよ？\nバイクなんてどこに……あ",
      "startTime": 182.8175962487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "気付いたか、バイクのシミュレーターがあるんだよ\nこれなら、本物に乗ってるみたいだろう？",
      "startTime": 189.4333319982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 192.1666735331
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます、{user}さん\nわぁ、バイクに乗るのなんて初めて……",
      "startTime": 195.5000068665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 200.0357122141
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、どうやって乗るといいんだろう……？\nこう？　ううん、違う……あ、こうかな？",
      "startTime": 205.6959464045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gamecenter-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gamecenter-00-noon",
      "startTime": 212.5023788808
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_07_02-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "……えい",
      "startTime": 212.5023788808,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
